snippet.title: EASA License B1/B2: What It Is, Requirements & How to Work as an Aircraft Mechanic in Europe
snippet.description:
Do you want to work as a certified aircraft mechanic in Europe?
In this video, we explain what the EASA license is, how it really works, and the correct steps to obtain it, regardless of your nationality or where you have worked before.

Many aircraft mechanics already have the required experience, but get stuck due to misinformation, poor documentation, or not knowing which EASA modules they actually need. This video clears up the confusion and shows you the right path.

✈️ In this video, you’ll learn:
- What the EASA License B1 and B2 is
- Whether non-European experience counts (yes, but it must be documented correctly)
- What EASA modules are and if you need to take all of them
- How to properly prepare your EASA logbook to avoid delays or rejection
- The most common mistakes that slow down the licensing process
- How to work as a certified aircraft mechanic in Europe after obtaining your license

At 360 Aviation Life, we guide aircraft mechanics from all over the world through the entire process:
- from evaluating your experience and defining the modules you really need,
- to exam preparation, logbook structuring, and correct submission of your EASA license application.

Our goal is simple: save you time, avoid costly mistakes, and help you move forward on the right path from day one.

👉 Want to know your exact path to the EASA License?

snippet.title: Kambodża Pol Pota  Ludobójstwo które narodziło się w salonach Paryża
snippet.description:
W imię komunistycznej utopii w Kambodży zamordowano ponad 25% społeczeństwa.
Pol Pot – wykształcony w Paryżu – stworzył jeden z najokrutniejszych reżimów XX wieku.
Ten film pokazuje, jak zachodnie idee doprowadziły do masowego ludobójstwa.
Historia, która przeraża – i zaskakuje swoją genezą.

Reżim Pol Pota i Czerwonych Khmerów był próbą stworzenia „idealnego” społeczeństwa bez miast, pieniędzy, własności prywatnej i edukacji. W praktyce oznaczało to głód, niewolniczą pracę i masowe egzekucje.

W filmie pokazujemy drogę Pol Pota – od studiów w Paryżu, fascynacji marksizmem i zachodnimi intelektualistami, po totalną zagładę własnego narodu. To także opowieść o międzynarodowym milczeniu, politycznych kalkulacjach i braku rozliczeń.

🔴 KOLEJNY LIVE we wtorek 10 lutego o godz. 20.00. Będziemy rozmawiać o tym jak Sowieci podporządkowali sobie Polskę w czasie II wojny światowej i po jej zakończeniu. Przeanalizujemy kluczowe momenty, mechanizmy i głównych graczy -  kolaborantów, zdrajców, matrioszek.

✨ Program LIVE i udział w dyskusji "na żywo" będzie dostępny tylko dla osób WPIERAJĄCYCH. Zachęcamy do dołączenia do klubu osób WPIERAJĄCYCH kanał "Zakazane Historie": https://youtu.be/dTXljcjk1dc

ZA TYDZIEŃ
📌 Jak wyglądały relacje Adolfa Hitlera z kobietami, które były mu najbliższe?

Ten film pokazuje nieznane kulisy prywatnego życia wodza III Rzeszy.
Fascynacja, chorobliwa zazdrość, manipulacja i próby samobójcze kobiet z jego otoczenia.
Oddzielamy fakty od mitów i pytamy, co naprawdę kryło się za tą mroczną historią.

W filmie opowiadamy o kobietach, które odegrały szczególną rolę w życiu Hitlera – od artystek i fanatycznych wyznawczyń ideologii, po młode kobiety uwikłane w dramatyczne, często tragiczne relacje. Analizujemy relacje, świadectwa, sprzeczne relacje świadków oraz hipotezy dotyczące zdrowia i psychiki dyktatora.

📌 To historia o władzy, obsesji i samotności człowieka, który zniszczył Europę.

snippet.description:
Estados Unidos dice que flexibiliza, pero en realidad aprieta de otra forma. La llamada Licencia General 47 no es un gesto de buena voluntad ni una rectificación histórica: es un intento sofisticado de volver a meter la mano en el petróleo venezolano. Washington autoriza diluyentes, contratos y exportaciones… pero al mismo tiempo dicta con quién puede y con quién no puede comerciar Caracas. Rusia no, China no, Cuba no. Negocia, pero bajo mis reglas. Produce, pero para mis intereses.
El objetivo es evidente: reinsertar a Venezuela en el mercado energético global, sí, pero desconectándola de sus aliados estratégicos, especialmente de China, que durante años sostuvo la industria petrolera venezolana cuando EE. UU. apostó al colapso. No es ayuda, es reposicionamiento geopolítico.

• Vehicle-based and foot-mobile use

snippet.description:
Meshtastic is a DIY radio text-messaging system that's been gaining popularity recently. It relies on community-maintained infrastructure instead of corporate or government networks. 

It's been claimed that Meshtastic is great for emergencies or social disruption, but is this really the case? And what's the best Meshtastic device? What settings should you use? These are all frequent questions I get, and which I'll try to address in this video. 

MSP Mesh info and settings can be found here: https://mspmesh.org/
Meshtastic general info and firmware flashing can be found here: https://meshtastic.org/

Some of the devices I showed in this video include:
T-Deck Plus (my overall favorite): https://amzn.to/49POFwM
T-Pager: https://amzn.to/4kbRpIj
Original T-Deck: https://lilygo.cc/products/t-deck-meshtastic

Meshnology antenna: https://amzn.to/3NIVW93

snippet.title: E1A NCVEC Extra Question Pool 2023-2027 for FCC General Radio License
snippet.description:
E1A Frequency privileges; signal frequency range; automatic message forwarding; stations aboard ships or aircraft; power restriction on 630- and 2200-meter bands
 
E1A01 (D) [97.305, 97.307(b)]
Why is it not legal to transmit a 3 kHz bandwidth USB signal with a carrier frequency of 14.348 MHz?
D. The upper 1 kHz of the signal is outside the 20-meter band
 
E1A02 (D) [97.301, 97.305]
When using a transceiver that displays the carrier frequency of phone signals, which of the following displayed frequencies represents the lowest frequency at which a properly adjusted LSB emission will be totally within the band?
D. 3 kHz above the lower band edge
 
E1A03 (C) [97.305, 97.307(b)]
What is the highest legal carrier frequency on the 20-meter band for transmitting a 2.8 kHz wide USB data signal?
C. 14.1472 MHz
 
E1A04 (C) [97.301, 97.305]
May an Extra class operator answer the CQ of a station on 3.601 MHz LSB phone?
C. No, the sideband components will extend beyond the edge of the phone band segment
 
E1A05 (C) [97.5]
Who must be in physical control of the station apparatus of an amateur station aboard any vessel or craft that is documented or registered in the United States?
C. Any person holding an FCC issued amateur license or who is authorized for alien reciprocal operation

 
E1A06 (B) [97.303(h)(1)]
What is the required transmit frequency of a CW signal for channelized 60 meter operation?
B. At the center frequency of the channel

 
E1A07 (C) [97.313(k)]
What is the maximum power permitted on the 2200-meter band?
C. 1 watt EIRP (equivalent isotropic radiated power)
 
E1A08 (B) [97.219]
If a station in a message forwarding system inadvertently forwards a message that is in violation of FCC rules, who is primarily accountable for the rules violation?
B. The control operator of the originating station
 
E1A09 (D) [97.313(l)]
Except in some parts of Alaska, what is the maximum power permitted on the 630-meter band?
D. 5 watts EIRP (equivalent isotropic radiated power)

 
E1A10 (A) [97.11]
If an amateur station is installed aboard a ship or aircraft, what condition must be met before the station is operated?
A. Its operation must be approved by the master of the ship or the pilot in command of the aircraft
 
E1A11 (B) [97.5]
What licensing is required when operating an amateur station aboard a US-registered vessel in international waters?
B. Any FCC-issued amateur license

snippet.title: Radio Blackouts Hit Australia as 'Solar Flare Fact
snippet.description:
Australia went dark. New Zealand lost communications. And the sun just won't stop firing.

Welcome to the most intense solar event of 2026 so far. In the past 48 hours, a single sunspot region has unleashed over 40 powerful solar flares, including an unprecedented X8.3-class eruption that triggered complete radio blackouts across the entire South Pacific.

This isn't just affecting amateur radio enthusiasts - critical aviation and maritime communication infrastructure went offline across an entire hemisphere. Ham radio operators in Australia and New Zealand experienced total signal loss below 30 MHz for hours. Dead air. Complete electromagnetic silence.

🌞 WHAT'S HAPPENING:

Sunspot region 4366 emerged out of nowhere last weekend and rapidly evolved into what space weather experts are calling a "solar flare factory." This volatile active region has fired off 1 C-class flare, 36 M-class flares, and 4 X-class flares in just two days - an absolutely relentless bombardment that shows no signs of stopping.
⚠️ WHY THIS MATTERS:

This sunspot has developed a Beta-Gamma-Delta magnetic configuration - the most volatile and explosive structure the sun can produce. These twisted, tangled magnetic field lines are snapping and releasing enormous amounts of energy over and over again like a machine gun.

Current forecasts show a 99% probability of C-class flares, 80% chance of M-class flares, and 40% probability of another X-class flare in the next 24 hours. That's not a remote possibility - that's a coin flip.

And here's the critical detail: this region is rotating into optimal Earth-facing position. Any future eruptions have a direct shot at our planet.

🌍 REAL-WORLD IMPACTS:

- Complete radio blackouts across Australia and New Zealand
- Aviation communication disruptions over the Pacific
- Maritime navigation system failures
- Emergency services coordination challenges
- Long-distance commercial radio links offline
- Potential GPS and satellite communication issues ahead

🔬 THE CARRINGTON CONNECTION:

Sunspot 4366 is now half the size of the infamous Carrington sunspot from 1859 - the most powerful geomagnetic storm in recorded history that set telegraph systems on fire worldwide. While we haven't seen confirmed Earth-directed coronal mass ejections yet, the rapid growth, extreme magnetic complexity, and sustained X-class flaring are all warning signs.

Despite producing flares from M1 to X8.3 levels, there's been no clear evidence of major CMEs so far. This is unusual and could mean the magnetic configuration is producing contained explosions - or the CMEs are oriented away from our detection angles. Either scenario could change rapidly.

💡 WHAT YOU SHOULD DO:

If you're in Australia, New Zealand, or anywhere across the South Pacific:
- Monitor space weather forecasts closely
- Have backup communication systems ready
- Don't rely exclusively on HF radio for critical operations
- Prepare for potential GPS disruptions

For everyone else:
- Keep devices charged and have backup power ready
- Stay hydrated - geomagnetic activity affects your nervous system
- Get adequate rest - electromagnetic fluctuations can disrupt sleep patterns
- Practice grounding techniques and stress management
- If you have cardiovascular conditions or pacemakers, be extra aware

⚡ WHAT'S NEXT:

The next 72 hours are critical. This solar flare factory is still firing, still growing, and rotating into perfect alignment for Earth-directed eruptions. We're monitoring this situation in real-time and will continue bringing you updates as new data comes in.

Solar maximum is far from finished, and the sun is speaking loudly.

snippet.title: US plans to issue licenses allowing companies to pump Venezuelan oil.
snippet.description:
Reports say the U.S. Department of the Treasury—through OFAC—is preparing a new general license that would let U.S. companies pump and extract oil directly in Venezuela, expanding beyond the permissions in General License 46.
General License 46 (issued January 29, 2026) already authorizes certain dealings with Venezuelan-origin crude—such as buying/selling, transport, storage, and refining—under specified compliance controls.
The upcoming license is described as a further easing step (moving from case-by-case permissions toward broader authorization), with supporters arguing it could help attract investment and raise output—while details and conditions are still emerging.
